        <p><strong>Question 1:</strong> Where was our family originally from? <br>
        <strong>Answer:</strong> Our family comes from different places, mainly from Nahariya and other areas in Israel.</p>
        <p><strong>Question 2:</strong> Do we have any special traditions or customs? <br>
        <strong>Answer:</strong> Yes! We celebrate Shabbat every week, and we always have family gatherings on holidays.</p>
